https://youtu.be/xOnMcdT2L0Q
This combination is from late 2016 to now, please be aware that some of the language in parts of this are offensive, crude, and childish (especially in the earliest clips). It was back then that I had realized my mind had been on #lockdown from all of the poisons I had been filled with, and I was attempting to process and explain...the process I was working through.

Are we not each a work in progress?

The reason for the mixture of past and recent video, and multiple topics, is to try and show that change is possible, doable, and worth every bit of the pain and discomfort from getting those poisons out (another work in progress).I have more or less been in a self imposed #quarantine since the #virus of darkness lost it's icy grip on my heart and mind, because I can clearly see whom it still holds...and it is many. This video is for them, as I feel that each has the ability to overcome the darkness when its manifestations are made known. Each also have the free will to knowingly continue serving darkness, though the devastating physical and mental toll it takes seems to be getting exponentially more potent and obvious. Stop, reflect, and change course while there is time.

Thank you for the gift of your time.
